@startuml system_state
!theme plain
title System State Chart Diagram

[*] --> Initializing

Initializing --> Starting : loadConfiguration()\n[Load system configuration]

Starting --> DatabaseConnecting : connectDatabase()\n[Establish database connection]

DatabaseConnecting --> AIModelLoading : databaseConnected()\n[Database connection successful]
DatabaseConnecting --> DatabaseError : connectionFailed()\n[Database connection failed]

AIModelLoading --> Running : modelsLoaded()\n[AI models loaded successfully]
AIModelLoading --> ModelError : modelLoadFailed()\n[AI model loading failed]

Running --> MaintenanceMode : enterMaintenance()\n[Admin triggers maintenance]
Running --> Overloaded : systemOverload()\n[System resources exceeded]
Running --> DatabaseError : databaseDisconnected()\n[Database connection lost]

MaintenanceMode --> Running : exitMaintenance()\n[Maintenance complete]

Overloaded --> Running : loadReduced()\n[System load normalized]
Overloaded --> Emergency : criticalOverload()\n[Critical system overload]

DatabaseError --> DatabaseConnecting : reconnectDatabase()\n[Attempt database reconnection]
DatabaseError --> Emergency : criticalDatabaseError()\n[Critical database failure]

ModelError --> AIModelLoading : reloadModels()\n[Retry model loading]
ModelError --> Emergency : criticalModelError()\n[Critical AI model failure]

Emergency --> Shutdown : emergencyShutdown()\n[Emergency system shutdown]

Running --> Shutdown : normalShutdown()\n[Normal system shutdown]
MaintenanceMode --> Shutdown : shutdownFromMaintenance()\n[Shutdown during maintenance]

Shutdown --> [*] : systemStopped()\n[System completely stopped]

' Self-transitions
Running --> Running : processRequest()\n[Handle user requests]
Running --> Running : performBackup()\n[Automated backup]
MaintenanceMode --> MaintenanceMode : updateSystem()\n[Apply system updates]

' Notes
note right of Initializing
  System starting up
  Loading core components
end note

note right of Running
  Normal operation
  All services available
end note

note right of MaintenanceMode
  Planned maintenance
  Limited functionality
end note

note right of Overloaded
  High system load
  Performance degraded
end note

note right of Emergency
  Critical system state
  Immediate action required
end note

note right of DatabaseError
  Database issues
  Data operations affected
end note

note right of ModelError
  AI model problems
  Predictions unavailable
end note

@enduml